      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "你讲。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021362022-05-20",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "江花右"
      ],
      "text": "我。不不……讲。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "啊！你这丫头，今日为何颠三倒四，敢是疯了不成？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "百花公主剑鞘击桌，惊起海俊。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "吓！（唱）啊呀唬！唬得我魂飞胆摇，望恕却残生这遭。亦非是越墙之盗，亦非是挟匕的那英豪，披肝胆敢装奸狡。",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "觑他容貌非奸狡，俊堂堂一貌丰标。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "唱江花右",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
