      "text": "唱",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "唱唗！既不是越墙之盗，因甚事潜身来到？将此事诉根苗，少时刻一命难逃！呔！那一汉子，家住哪里？姓甚名谁？快快讲来！是，是，是。公主容禀！恨无端生出祸根苗。𠲔！可恨那叭喇呵！唔！你是甚等样人，敢言我内侍叭喇？是啊！你是甚等样人，敢言我内侍叭喇？是，是，是。哪！他忌才能暗藏机巧。小生海俊，新任西府参军。不想内侍叭喇，假意庆贺为由，将酒把我灌醉呵。不知怎么到了公主内庭，内庭上来了。哎呀公主呀！恕微臣误入在蓬岛。（白）啊哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 212
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "唔！你深夜潜入内庭，理当问斩，念你中了他人之计，我就不杀你了。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "江花右"
      ],
      "text": "快快谢了公主！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "是，是，是。多谢公主！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "只是便宜了你。江花右！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "江花右"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "看看哪里粉墙可越，送他出去。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "江花右"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀且住！我看公主倒有爱我哥哥之意，唔，我自有道理。正是：（念）闭门推出窗前月……",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "啊妹子，你送我出去呀！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "江花右"
      ],
      "text": "嗳！（念）吩咐梅花自主张。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "江花右下。百花公主",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "江花右"
      ],
      "text": "你还未曾去么？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "未曾。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "江花右呢？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "不知去向。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "待我唤来。啊江花右！江花右！这丫头不知往哪里去了。啊海生，深夜无人，待我送你出去。海俊",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "多谢公主。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "就在此攀梅而过。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "有劳公主。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "海生。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021362022-05-20",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "休将老梅来折损，待他乘月泄春光。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "啊？那公主为何道此两句？唔，莫非她有爱我之意呀？唔，我且闪过一旁，听她讲些什么。有理吓有理！",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖起三更鼓〗。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00066",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "想那海生，言语清朗，气度轩昂。我有意将终身托付与他，怎奈女孩儿家，羞人答答，不好启齿。吖有了！待我稟过父王，方好成其美事。啊呀……好个海生！好个海生！",
      "text_length": 75
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00067",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "海生在！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00068",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00069",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "雁儿落",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "广寒岑寂，仙子思飘遥，须知道桂蕊向少年抛。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00070",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖雅笛〗。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00071",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花公主"
      ],
      "text": "海生，我不杀你，你心中可明白？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902136_e00072",
      "play_id": "70902136",
      "scene_id": "70902136_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海俊"
      ],
      "text": "多蒙公主将终身相许，我是何以为报？何……以为报？",
